Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:25.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,真的吗?  他们不是要在最后时刻\NReally? are they looking into free agent signing at
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:26.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,签几名自由球员吗?\NThe last second or anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可能吧  他们有一支训练有素的球队\NPossibly, they got a strong farm club too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,随时让顶级球员替补上场\NThey got some aaa ball players they might be bringing up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,彼得在半小时之后\NBut again, peter will certianly be able tell us a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:34.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,会带来详细的报道\NMore about that in the next half hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你看好哪支队伍?\NWho do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,到现在为止  我看好纽约队的表现\NWell tell you, so far, I like what I'm seeing in new york.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们跟以前一样实力雄厚\NThey got a strong ball club as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:41.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这是美国最好的球队...\NThat is in the american, and..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:44.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在国家联盟里  我还是看好芝加哥\NAnd the national, I'm still liking chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:47.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,遇上洛杉矶会有点小麻烦\NWith a little bit of twist here for los angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好的  究竟纽约和芝加哥会师决赛\Nokay, so we're looking here at new york, chicago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:51.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,还是洛杉矶充当黑马\NWorld series, possible los angeles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这个赛季结束就能见分晓\NHey, hold it to him to the end of the season.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在让我们把镜头从体育播报\NThat's gonna do it from the sports desk for right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:58.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,切换回直播室  谢谢戴夫\NBack to you guys in the studio, thanks dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:01.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢  艾迪  谢谢大家\NThanks for nothing eddy, thank you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们关注的不止是这些\NThat's not all we're following.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:05.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在由凯伦带来健康播报\NHere's karen at the health desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:08.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,医药界已经见证了不少奇迹\NThe world of medicine has seen its share of miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:11.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,从小儿麻痹疫苗到心脏移植术\NCures from the polio vaccine to heart transplants.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:14.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但过去所有的成就相比于\NBut all past achievements may pale
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:16.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,爱丽丝·克里本医生的成果就显得黯然失色\NIn comparison to the work of dr. alice krippin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:18.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天上午接受我们的访问\Nthank you so much for joining us this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:19.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不客气\Nnot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:22.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,克里本医生  请您简单介绍一下\NDr. krippin, give it to me in a nutshell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:26.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,前提非常简单\NThe premise is quite simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:28.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,利用大自然创造的东西...\NTake something designed by nature ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:31.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,重新组合使其为人体\NAnd reprogram it to make it work for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:33.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,服务而不是与其作对\NThe body rather than against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.10,0:01:34.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你指的是病毒吗?\NYou're talking about a virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  这里是指麻疹病毒\Nindeed yes, in this case, the measles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:39.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,从基因层面改造这种病毒\NA virus which has been engineered at a genetic
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,会变得有用而非有害\NLevel to be helpful rather than harmful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我想到个很好的比喻\NI find the best way to describe it is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你把自己的身体想成是一条公路\NIf you can imagine your body is a highway....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:52.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,病毒就像是一辆快速行驶的汽车\NAnd you picked the virus as a very fast car,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:53.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,被一个坏家伙驾驶着\NBeing driven by a very bad man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:57.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,试想这辆车会带来多大的伤害\NImagine the damage that car can cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但如果你让一个警察来驾驶\NBut if you replace that man with a cop,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:01.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,情况就有所不同了\NThen the picture changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们实质上就是做这些事\NAnd that is essentially what we have done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,目前你们治疗了多少人?\Nand how many people have you treated so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:10.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,到现在我们做了10009个临床试验\NWe have 10,009 clinical trials in humans so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:11.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,多少人的癌症被治愈?\Nand how many are cancer free?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:14.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,10009\N10,009.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那么你们已经攻克了癌症?\Nso you have actually cured cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  是的  我们做到了\NYes yes, yes we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:26.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,本字幕由YYeTs人人影视字幕组原创翻译制作 www.YYeTs.net
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:31.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,三年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:16.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你看到了什么\NWhat do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,该死\NDamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:51.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们走  萨曼\NLet's go sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,去吃吧  你最喜欢的做法\NHere you go, just the way you like it....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好恶心\NDisgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:25.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,让一下\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:29.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,放松\NRelax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,吃吧\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别那样  蔬菜也得吃\NNo, eat your vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别拨来拨去的  吃掉它们\NDon't just push 'em around, eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:13.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我可没说笑\NI'm not playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,吃你的蔬菜\NEat your vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,否则就整晚坐在这里\NOr we'll sit down here all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你发什么牢骚?\NWhat are you whining about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:28.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,为什么不好好吃你的蔬菜?\NWhy didn't you just eat your vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧  听着  听着\NOkay, look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,明晚你必须要吃\NWe're gonna eat twice as many vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:33.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,双倍的蔬菜\NTomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,成交?\NDeal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:02.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,感觉不错吧\NThat feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼\NAh sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:18.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,罗伯特  出什么事儿了?  我一直\NRobert, what is happening? I've been trying
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,试着打你手机  总是转入语音信箱\NTo reach you on the cell, I keep getting the recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-网络断了  -爸爸  我们要去哪儿?\N- the network is down.             - dad, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我还是不习惯这身新装备\NI cannot get used to the new rags.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们要去莎拉阿姨家\Nwe're going to aunt sarah's sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不  为什么?\NNo, why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,自己系好安全带  走\Njust strap yourself in, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们只有30分钟  上校\Nwe're at 30 minutes colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,知道了\Ncopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,30分钟去做什么?\N30 minutes to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们要封锁这个岛\Nthey're sealing off the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,封锁这个岛?  这个岛?\Nseal off the island?  this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:44.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但我不想去莎拉阿姨家\Nbut I don't wanna go to aunt sarah's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:47.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你把钱都带上了吗?  有多少?\Ndid you bring all the money?  how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,600美元  你说"你们要走"什么意思?\N600 dollars, why did you say you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:50.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,钱还不够\Nthat is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,罗伯特  你说"你们要走"  而不是"我们要走"\Nrobert, you said "you're going", not "we're going".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,过去后  我要你找个取款机\Nwhen you get across, I need you to get to the atm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:55.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,能取多少就取多少\NGet as much cash as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在又不是夏天\Nit's not even summer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:13:59.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,开上莎拉的车  远离城市\Ntake sarah's car, go upstate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:02.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我会到农场接你们  带上足够两周的食物\NI'll meet you at the farm, bring enough food for 2 weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,天啊  罗伯特  病毒开始蔓延了?\NJesus, robert. did it jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,空气传播?\NIs it airborne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:10.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,可我们只在夏天才去莎拉阿姨家的\Nbut we only go to aunt sarah's in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有可能\Nmaybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:15.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,今天是圣诞节  我的礼物呢?\NIt's christmas. what about my presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:16.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,总统宣布着这件事\Nhe's announcing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:18.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不要搞错了  我的美国人民\Nmake no mistake my fellow americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我的礼物还在壁橱里  -突变的病毒是致命的\N- my gifts are still in the closet.        - the mutated virus is lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:22.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,安静点  玛丽\Nhush now mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,此事不仅关系到美国人民的生存\Nthe survival of not only our nation, but
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:25.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,还关系到全世界人民\NOf every other nation on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,妈妈  看啊  是一只蝴蝶\Nmom, look. a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,玛丽  够了\Nmarley, enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:32.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我怀着极为沉痛的心情和强烈的决心\NSo, I announce with great sadness, but even greater resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,今晚我签署一条行政命令\NThat tonight I have signed an executive order,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,对纽约启动军事隔离\NInitiating a military quarantine of new york city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:44.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,原上帝与我们同在\Ngod be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.60,0:14:51.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,还有机会  我们会有办法的  也许1  2礼拜内\Nthe window is still open, we find something in a week..or 2 weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:54.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,能够阻止病毒蔓延\N...we can reverse the spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我能解决这一切\NI can still fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:06.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,求你了  你能在市区外还是能做这些的\NPlease, you can do the same work outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:12.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,爆心投影点  这是我的区域  我们说过的\NGround zero, this is my site. we talked about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:15.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你要做什么?\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:19.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要做什么?\NWhat am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要阻止这一切的发生\NI'm not gonna let this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:26.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,什么?  这不是你能决定的  你不能\Nlet? this isn't up to you, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,睡好了吗?\NHow did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:22.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别进去  你知道的\NNow come on, you know better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我会回来的\NI'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:02.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,罗伯特·奈维尔博士  2012年9月5日  GA系列391号血清\NDr. robert neville, september 5, 2012. ga series serum 391.
