Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:29.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,下次用来做人体实验\NIs the next candidate for human trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,撑住啊  6号小鼠\NHang in there number 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:17.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,想开车窗就开吧\NYeah, that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:44.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,早安  玛姬  早安  弗雷德\NGood morning, marge and fred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你们这么早来干什么啊?\NWhat are you doing here so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,弗雷德  运动衫不错啊\NNice sweatshirt there fred.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:51.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别把它乱放\NDon't fit it down anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们里面见\NI see you inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,怎么了  伙计?\NWhat's happening brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:53.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,早上好  汉克\NGood morning hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,通过G测试了\NGetting through the g's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那个女孩是谁\NWho's the girl ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,算了  明早见吧\NNevermind, hey I'll see you in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我该怎么打招呼呢?\N- what am I supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你好  想看看被感染的老鼠吗\N- hello, wanna see some infected rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:25.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好吧  就明天\NOkay, tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,明天我就去和她打招呼\NI'm going to say hello tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,干得好\NYou did so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:57.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就这样\NYes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:02.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,看看  看见没有?  红鲑鱼罐头\NLook at that, see that?  red salmon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,噢  肉罐头\NWow, actual spam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你等下再吃\NNo, you'll get some of that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:22.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是罗伯特·奈维尔  我是纽约的一名幸存者\NI am robert neville. I am a survivor
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.20,0:24:28.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我在AM所有频道上进行广播\NI am broadcasting on all am frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.40,0:24:32.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,每天中午我都会在南大街码头\NI will be at the south street seaport everyday
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.20,0:24:43.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果你能听到我  如果任何人能听到我\NIf you are out there...if anyone is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:50.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我能提供食物  我能提供住所\NI can provide food, I can provide shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:51.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我能提供安全保障\NI can provide security.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.60,0:24:58.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果有任何人能听到我  任何人\NIf there is anybody out there, anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:03.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请回答我  你不是孤独一人\NPlease, you are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:39.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好好看我这球\NKeep your eye on this one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.60,0:25:51.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我打得越来越好了\NI'm getting good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.40,0:27:52.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,来吧萨曼  必须得走了  必须得走了\NCome on sam. I gotta go. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.70,0:31:02.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼  出来  我们得走了\NSam, come on. we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.20,0:31:06.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你在干什么?\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.30,0:31:19.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼  我们快走!\NSam, we gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.00,0:31:30.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼  快走  快出去!\NSam, go now, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.50,0:32:31.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你一定要小心  知道吗?\NYou need to pay attention, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.00,0:32:31.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-要小心点\N- gotta pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:37.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,听着  这次我要你乖乖地待在这\NListen, I want you to stay here on this one, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.80,0:32:45.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,因为你仍会被感染  而我不会\NBecause you can still get infected and I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.90,0:33:07.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,听着  如果天黑了我还没回来\NListen, if I am not back by dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.50,0:33:12.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你就自己走吧\NJust go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.60,0:34:44.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,试验对象为女性\NOkay, the subject is female.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.80,0:34:48.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,大约18-20岁\NMost likely 18-20 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.00,0:34:52.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所需注射镇静剂剂量为正常人的6倍\Na lot of push effective 6 times the human dose.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.60,0:34:56.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,体温华氏106度  脉搏每分钟200\NCore temperature 106 fahrenheit, pulse 200 bpm,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.50,0:35:03.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,呼吸急促  动脉血氧含量为正常人3倍\N..respiration elevated, pao2 300% of normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.10,0:35:11.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,瞳孔已完全扩张\NThe pupils are fully dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.20,0:35:12.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,对光线有反应\NNow reactive to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.60,0:35:27.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,皮肤对紫外线有强烈反应\NExtreme reaction to uv exposure...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:30.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,症状和组织采样表明\NSymptoms and tissue samples confirm subject
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.30,0:35:33.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她已感染KV病毒\NIs infected with kv.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.40,0:35:42.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,391号血清疫苗试验  第6号化合物\NVaccine test series serum 391 compound six.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.70,0:35:43.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,开始人体试验\NCommencing human trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.90,0:36:12.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,呼吸开始变慢  脉搏190\NRespiration is slowing, pulse 190,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.80,0:36:19.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,体温105  104  继续降低\NCore temperature 105, 104 and decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.40,0:36:26.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好像有些效果了\NWe may have something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.60,0:37:14.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,GA系列391号血清疫苗第六号化合物  对人体无效\NGa series serum 391 compound 6,ineffective on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:36.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,试验结果存入链接在此机的\NTest results linked to this entry,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.60,0:37:39.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,6个备份硬盘里\NSaved on 6 redundant drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.20,0:37:42.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,依然无效\NStill no cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.00,0:38:03.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,第1001天  今天我们近距离接触一个巢穴\NDay 1001: we came in close contact with a hive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.10,0:38:06.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,血液试验表明  我仍然对\NThe blood tests confirm that I remain immune....
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.60,0:38:10.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,空气性和接触性传播免疫\NFor both the airborne and contact strains.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.90,0:38:17.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,犬类仅对空气性传播免疫\NCanines remain immune to airborne strain only.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.70,0:38:22.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,傻瓜  你不能跑到阴暗的地方去\NYou can't go running into the dark dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.40,0:38:26.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,疫苗试验继续  可我依然无法\NVaccine trials continue.  I am still unable
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.10,0:38:27.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,将我自己的免疫能力\NTo transfer my immunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.70,0:38:34.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,转移到被感染者的身上去  KV病毒  真的很奇妙\N...to infected host.  krippin virus is....elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.80,0:38:43.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就像在大海捞针\NIt's like fishing in the dark, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.80,0:38:52.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,今天一个被感染女性\NUm, an infected male
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.30,0:38:54.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,将自己暴露在日光下\NExposed himself to sunlight today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.00,0:39:02.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,有可能大脑功能退化  或是\NNow it's possible that decreased brain function..or...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.20,0:39:03.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,因为食物缺乏\NGrowing scarcity of food is..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.30,0:39:09.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,导致他们忽视自己的求生本能\N...is causing them to ignore their basic survival instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.50,0:39:18.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,社交能力退化已很明显\NSocial de-evolution appears complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.00,0:39:21.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,典型人类行为已完全消失\NTypical human behavior is now entirely absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.30,0:39:32.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们为什么停下来?\NWhy are we stopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.30,0:39:38.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请出来\NPlease go
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.00,0:39:38.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你们只有不到10分钟时间\N- you've got less than 10 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.70,0:39:41.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,宝贝  把狗给我\NBaby, give me the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.50,0:39:46.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我们走  宝贝  我们走\N- let's go baby, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.10,0:39:47.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-爸爸\N- daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.30,0:39:52.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,待在那附近  别让任何人靠近\NStay in my neighborhood and let nobody stop you by.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.90,0:39:54.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-妈妈  他们有枪\N- mommy, they have guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.70,0:39:58.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-别担心  他们像爸爸一样也是军人\N- it's okay, they're in the army like daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.10,0:40:04.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请回家去\NThen, please, back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.50,0:40:06.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-过来\N- coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.30,0:40:49.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果你没有通过检查\NIf you are not covered by the checkpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.20,0:40:52.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那么  请回吧\NThen, please, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.40,0:40:59.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你没问题  往前走\NYou're clear. go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.80,0:41:01.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-通过\N- clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.10,0:41:08.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,通过  好吧  下一个  继续走\NClear...okay, next, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.60,0:41:12.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不行\NNo good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.00,0:41:21.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,通过  -走\NClear - okay, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.60,0:41:25.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我们没被感染\N- we are not infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.00,0:41:26.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-请带走我的女儿\N- please, please take my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.70,0:41:29.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,退后退\NYou have to move back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.40,0:41:33.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没通过\NNo good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.10,0:41:34.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-什么?  不!  罗伯特  罗伯特!\N- what, no!  robert, robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.20,0:41:40.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,手拿开  别碰我太太\NWhoa, whoa, get your hands off my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.90,0:41:43.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是罗伯特·奈维尔上校\NI'm lieutenant robert neville
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.80,0:41:46.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,把手拿开\NGet your hands off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.70,0:41:48.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-再扫描她一遍\N- scan her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.70,0:41:49.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-退后!\N- stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.70,0:41:52.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-退后士兵!  退后!\N- stand down soldier! stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:53.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我是陆军上校罗伯特·奈维尔\N- I am lieutenant-colonel robert neville.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.60,0:41:56.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我命令你再扫描她一遍\NI order you to scan her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.20,0:41:58.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,再扫描她一遍!\NScan her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.40,0:42:04.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-好吧  再扫描一遍\N- alright, scan her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.50,0:42:09.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,通过  没问题  过去吧\NClear, it's clear, move through.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.50,0:42:23.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,爸爸  我们为什么不能回自己的家?\NDad, why can't we go to our home too?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.30,0:42:29.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-还有多久?\N- how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.80,0:42:31.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-5分钟  来得及\N- five minutes, we'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.50,0:42:35.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,621  我们已到\N621. we are on site.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.50,0:42:53.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我会好好照顾她们的  上校\NI won't take my eyes off them colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.50,0:42:55.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我向你保证\NYou got my word on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.00,0:43:03.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,亲一下\NGive me a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.40,0:43:14.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,小心点  -你也是\NBe careful. - you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.00,0:43:19.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-上帝啊  请保佑罗伯特\N- dear god, please watch over robert,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.60,0:43:21.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,赋予他勇气去战胜一切难题\NKeep him strong for the struggle ahead of him lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.80,0:43:25.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请把他安全地带回来  阿门\NPlease, just bring him home safely, amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.90,0:43:29.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,爸爸去把那些怪物消灭掉  好吗?\NDaddy's going to make the monsters go away baby, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.70,0:43:32.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-萨曼  你去保护爸爸\N- sam, you protect daddy.
