Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.90,0:43:36.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,长官  我们得走了\NSir, we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.80,0:43:41.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,爸爸  你看  一只蝴蝶\NDad, look, a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.50,0:44:39.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你睡得怎么样?  -罗伯特·奈维尔博士正在仔细观察\N- how'd you sleep?     - dr. robert neville will be taking a closer look
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.40,0:44:42.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,爱丽丝·克里本博士研究的病毒变化\N...at the ongoing mutations of dr. alice krippin's
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.80,0:44:45.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那曾经一度奇迹般治愈癌症\NOnce hailed miracle cure for cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.70,0:44:49.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,到目前为止  大约5000名病人感染变种的病毒\NSo far, almost 5000 patients treated with a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.00,0:44:52.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们已经显现出类似早期狂犬病症状\NRetrofitted virus, had begun exhibiting symptoms
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.30,0:44:57.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,目前已有25名病人死亡\N25 patients have already died.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.50,0:44:59.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,奈维尔博士已命令当地医院储存好抗病毒药物\NDr. neville has ordered local hospitals to stockpile
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.00,0:45:04.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,并准备实施初步的检疫隔离方案\NAntiviral drugs, and to begin preliminary quarantine protocol....
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.70,0:45:06.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-今天是我生日\N- it's my birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.70,0:45:09.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-我们完全相信奈维尔博士能带领我们...\N- we are fully confident dr. neville can see us through...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.90,0:45:12.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-想唱歌吗?\N- would you like to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.60,0:45:18.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是罗伯特·奈维尔  我是纽约的一名幸存者\NMy name is robert neville, I am a survivor living in new york city.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.80,0:45:24.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我在AM所有频道上进行广播\NI am broadcasting on all am frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.10,0:45:29.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,每天中午我都会在南大街码头\NI will be at the south street seaport everyday, midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.50,0:45:32.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,中午艳阳高照的时候\NWhen the sun is highest in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.00,0:45:37.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果你能听到我  如果任何人能听到我\NIf you are out there....if anyone is out there....
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.20,0:45:43.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我能提供食物  我能提供住所\NI can provide food, I can provide shelter,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.10,0:45:44.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我能提供安全保障\NI can provide security.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.50,0:45:49.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果有任何人能听到我  任何人\NIf there's anybody out there, anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.40,0:45:55.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请回答我  你不是孤独一人\NPlease, you are not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.80,0:46:01.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,听着  如果你想要开个聚会或是其他什么\NListen, if you're planning a party or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.30,0:46:02.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,现在就告诉我\NJust tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.80,0:46:06.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,因为我并不喜欢惊喜  但我发誓\NOkay, because I don't like surprises, and I swear
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.20,0:46:09.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我能表现得很惊讶  好吗?\NI'll act surprised. okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.60,0:46:56.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,弗雷德  你在这里干什么?\NWhat are you doing out here fred?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.30,0:47:03.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你在这搞什么鬼  不!\NWhat the hell are you.....no!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.30,0:47:04.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-不  不!\N- no! no!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.80,0:47:09.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,弗雷德  你究竟在这儿干嘛?\NWhat the hell are you doing out here fred!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.30,0:47:10.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你怎么到这儿来的?\NHow did you get out here?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.30,0:47:14.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,弗雷德  如果你还活着  最好马上告诉我!\NFred, if you're real, you better tell me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.80,0:47:19.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果你还活着  最好马上告诉我!\NIf you're real, you better tell me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.20,0:47:34.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他妈的  弗雷德\NDamn, fred.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.50,0:49:40.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我没事\NI'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.20,0:50:09.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我没事\NI'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.70,0:50:37.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我没事\NI'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.20,0:52:00.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,过来  萨曼\NCome on, sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.40,0:52:01.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,过来\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.50,0:52:18.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼  我们走!\NLet's go sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.80,0:52:30.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼  快走  我们得回家了\NNo, no, let's go sam, we gotta go home sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.30,0:52:34.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.90,0:53:44.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你没事的\NOkay, you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.10,0:53:48.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你没事的  你没事的\NIt's okay. you're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.00,0:53:49.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你一定会没事儿的\NYou're alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.20,0:53:51.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼塔  萨曼塔\NSamantha, samantha.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.80,0:53:55.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,看着我  宝贝  你不会有事的\NLook at me girl. hey, you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.90,0:53:59.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,萨曼塔  我带你回家\NSamantha, just gotta get you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.80,0:54:02.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,带你回家  带你回家\NGotta take you home, take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.00,0:54:05.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,好了  来吧\NAlright, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.10,0:54:45.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,到这儿来  好样的\NCome here, come here, got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.50,0:54:54.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没事儿的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.40,0:58:55.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我向朋友保证  会和你\NI promised my friend.... that I would say hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.60,0:58:56.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,今天打招呼的\NTo you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.80,0:59:26.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请和我问好啊\NPlease say hello to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.60,0:59:36.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,请和我问好啊\NPlease say hello to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.50,1:00:59.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,去死!\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.70,1:01:16.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,去死!\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.00,1:03:03.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,听见我说话吗?\NCan you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.80,1:03:11.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,坚持一下\NStick with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.80,1:03:14.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你住哪儿?\NWhere you live?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.00,1:03:19.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你住哪儿?\NWhere you live?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.10,1:03:23.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,11号\NEleven...Eleven
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.50,1:03:27.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,华盛顿广场11号\NWashington and square.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.10,1:03:28.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们不知道我住哪儿\NThey don't know where I live.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.10,1:03:34.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,别让他们追踪到\NDon't let them track us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.90,1:03:36.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等到清晨再回去\NYou must stay in till dawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.80,1:06:31.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,恐怕鸡蛋煎的太烂了\NI'm afraid the eggs are powdered, obviously
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.10,1:06:33.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不过你知道的  这份是你的\NYou know that.  they're yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.80,1:06:37.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但我竟然找到了培根\NBut I did find bacon.  I just found the most
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.30,1:06:38.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这可能是史上最好的事儿了\NFantastic thing in history.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.80,1:06:43.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我还在浴室里找到些抗生素\NI found some antibiotics in the bathroom, I put
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.60,1:06:45.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,食物盛在你盘子里了  你的腿好的差不多了\NBy your plate because your leg is okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.80,1:06:47.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但如果不及时开始治疗\NBut you won't be for very long, if you don't
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.80,1:06:50.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,情况会变得糟糕的\NStart a course very soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.80,1:06:54.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你是谁?\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.70,1:06:56.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我是安娜  这是伊桑\NI am anna and this is ethan.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.90,1:07:07.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,不吃这些要凉了\NThey're going to get cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.90,1:07:21.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,没事儿  你坐啊\NIt's okay.  go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.80,1:07:48.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们来自马里兰州\NWe come from maryland.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.90,1:07:51.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们听到了你的广播\NWe heard your message heard on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.70,1:07:56.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们中午就到了码头  在那儿等了你一天\NWe were at the pier at noon, we waited all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.60,1:08:00.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们打算去佛蒙特州\NWe're going to vermont.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.20,1:08:01.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那个幸存者隔离区\NTo the survivor's colony.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.60,1:08:08.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在贝索尔市  那是个安全的地方\NIn bethel. it is a safe zone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.40,1:08:12.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,根本没有幸存者隔离区  更别说安全的地方了\NThere's no survivor's colony, no safe zone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.60,1:08:14.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,整件事没按原计划发展\NNothing's happening the way it was supposed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.20,1:08:16.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,也没按原计划执行\NNothing worked the way it was supposed to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.60,1:08:19.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,在山上  有一群没有被感染的人\Nin the mountains, there is a whole colony of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.20,1:08:21.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,建成的隔离区\NPeople there who didn't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.10,1:08:23.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,病毒不能在寒冷的环境里滋长蔓延\NThe virus couldn't survive the cold, there's a whole...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.70,1:08:26.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,闭嘴!\Nshut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.10,1:08:30.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,所有人都死了\NEverybody's dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.90,1:08:41.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,让我静一下好吗?\NI just need a minute, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.60,1:08:45.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我只是\NJust....
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.00,1:08:52.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我一直留着那块培根\NI just, I was saving that bacon.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.70,1:08:55.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一直留着舍不得吃\NI was saving it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.60,1:08:59.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我要上楼去了\NI'm gonna go upstairs, alright, just.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.80,1:09:00.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我得上去了\NI'm gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.60,1:09:22.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,伊桑  把刀放下\NEthan, put that knife down.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.50,1:10:29.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,能和你说话吗?\Ncan I say something to you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.80,1:10:32.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你刚才真的太不可思议了\NYou was really really something back there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.90,1:10:36.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你在和...我说话?\NAre you talking to...me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.50,1:10:42.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  你对付那些侍卫时真厉害\NCan I tell you that you were great? those guards.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.70,1:10:44.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们自以为很强\NThey thought that they were tough.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.40,1:10:48.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,但是你一出现他们就全跑了\NAnd when you came and they were nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.50,1:10:49.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,真有意思\NThat was fun to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.60,1:10:52.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,感觉棒极了  自由的感觉真好\NThat's great. seriously.    -- it is nice to be free.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.50,1:10:55.10,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,去和你的朋友庆祝自由吧\NWhy don't you celebrate your freedom
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.10,1:10:57.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,和朋友一同去?\NWith your own friends?  hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.30,1:11:02.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我没有朋友  我也不想\NBut I have no friends. and I am not going
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.90,1:11:03.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,单独一个人走\NOut there by myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.40,1:11:06.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,等下  我有个好主意\NWait, I have a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.20,1:11:08.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我可以和你一起走\NI'll stick with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.50,1:11:18.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我喜欢史瑞克\NI like shrek.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.30,1:11:36.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你不太记得如何与人相处了  对吗?\NYou are not as good with people anymore are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.50,1:11:44.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢你为我处理伤口\NThank you for my leg.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.40,1:11:53.50,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你都经历了些什么?\NWhere have you been?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.50,1:11:56.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我之前在圣保罗的红十字会救援船\NI was on a red cross evacuation ship out of saint paolo.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.90,1:12:00.60,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,那些船不会支撑太久的\Nthose boats weren't meant to be permanent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.60,1:12:01.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,是的  没错\Nno they weren't.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.90,1:12:04.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,当那些海军被干掉后  我们去船上抢供给\NWhen the navy fell apart, we set on dock to get supplies.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.90,1:12:07.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,一些人在岸上被感染了\NSomeone picked it up on shore.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.80,1:12:08.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我们有五人免疫\N5 of us were immune.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.90,1:12:13.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,-你说有五人  -他们被追随者捉住了\NYou said five. -- the dark seekers got them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.20,1:12:19.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你是罗伯特·奈维尔  对吗?\NYou are the robert neville, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.50,1:12:30.90,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,今天太晚了  如果我们明天清晨出发\NIt's too late today. if we leave tomorrow at dawn,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.90,1:12:32.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,就可以一路驱车到达佛蒙特州\NWe can make it to vermont in a straight shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.20,1:12:33.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,如果...\NSo if we ...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.20,1:12:35.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不会离开的\NI'm not leaving.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.70,1:12:41.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,这是"爆心投影点"  我的地盘\NThis is ground zero. this is my site.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.20,1:12:46.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我不会让病毒肆虐的\NI'm not gonna let this happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.00,1:12:51.20,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我还能补救\NI can still fix this.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.00,1:13:06.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,你吓到我了\NOh, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.70,1:13:07.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,抱歉\Nsorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.80,1:13:09.70,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我喊了两次都没反映\NI called down twice.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.70,1:13:11.00,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,谢谢你\Noh thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.80,1:13:20.40,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,她打了重度镇静剂  别担心  很安全的\NThat's heavily sedated, don't worry it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.40,1:13:24.30,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,我从未见过他们如此平静\NI've never seen one so still.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.30,1:13:25.80,*Default,说话人,0,0,0,,他们总是攻击咬人\NThey're always biting.
